        "text_iYf8VY": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Anxious Preoccupied was founded by Joanne McNally and Nikki Lannen, best friends of 15 years who turned years of \"we could do this better\" into something real.</p><p>This brand is for the modern woman who knows who she is, even when everything around her is a lot. Our pieces are for women who like to be noticed without trying to be. Not loud for the sake of it, not attention-seeking. Just quietly confident, cool, and a little unexpected.</p><p>She loves detail. She loves a statement. She loves when someone says, \"Where did you get that?\"</p><p>She's also got ten tabs open, a voice note she hasn't listened to, and somewhere to be ten minutes ago. Her life is full, fast, and chaotic, and her accessories get that.</p>",
